title\">Persepolis</title_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1222.tlg001:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Beros.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16</biblScope> </bibl> (leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">[καὶ] π.</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0074.tlg001:3:18:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Arr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.18.10</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Περσέπολις</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n82665.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> freq. as pr.n., <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Perses\">Perses</a></title_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">27</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:61\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.61</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; name of a Titan, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:409\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">409</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n82665.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> the name of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a throw on the dice</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bib